(2, 0, 'Alvas Ekalavya', '2012-06-12', '00:00:00', 'Dr. Alva has initiated yet another project which aims at facilitating sports arena in the state. It is a sporting extravaganza under floodlight during which time the entire town of Modabidri resemble a sports village with more than 6000 athletes from across the state take part right from primary school to university level. The Ekalavya club was established in 1988 to nurture talents in sports by adopting talented sports from various parts of the state and provided full scholarship which covers food, coaching, medical facilities and education. Several athletes of national and international fame have been groomed here which includes names like Mr. Sathish Rai who took part in Olympic Games, Jamaluddin, who represented India at the International level. Hundreds of them have set new records at inter-varsity, state level & national level and brought laurels to the club.');
